data.content:
verb
-tunes; -tuned; -tuning
[+ obj] :to cause (a person, company, etc.) to have a better understanding of what is needed or wanted by a particular person or group - usually + to
It is important to attune the company to the needs of its customers. - often used as (be) attuned
The company is attuned to the needs of its customers.
He is more attuned to the political climate of the region.

Động từ
(thường ở dạng bị động)
làm cho hợp với, làm cho quen với
we (our ears) are becoming attuned to the noise of the new factory nearby
[tai] chúng tôi đã trở nên quen với tiếng ồn của nhà máy mới ở gần bên
